title: Dead Men Walk 1943 | George Zucco, Mary Carlisle | Vampiric twin rises from cursed crypt!

sources.title: Dead Men Walk 1943 | George Zucco, Mary Carlisle | Vampiric twin rises from cursed crypt!
sources.description:
The twin of a kindly small-town physician returns from the grave for vengeance against his brother, who secretly killed him because the twin served Satan.

Director: Sam Newfield
Writer: Fred Myton 
Stars: George Zucco, Mary Carlisle, Nedrick Young 
Genres:  Horror, Mystery, Drama

00:00 - Full Movie (with subtitles) 
00:42 - Introduction to vampire lore and Dr. Clayton's conflict with his brother Elwyn.
04:08 - Dr. Clayton reveals Elwyn's malevolent history and mysterious death.
15:21 - Elwyn returns as a vampire, threatening Dr. Clayton and targeting Gayle.
23:02 - Gayle exhibits vampiric symptoms, prompting Dr. Clayton's desperate investigation.
32:35 - Dr. Clayton and Zolar devise a plan to destroy Elwyn's supernatural form.
44:38 - The discovery of Elwyn's hidden coffin exposes his vulnerability by daylight.
53:00 - Villagers confront Dr. Clayton, mistaking him for the murderer during a tense standoff.
57:17 - Dr. Clayton sacrifices himself in a fiery climax to vanquish Elwyn and save Gayle.
